snippet.title: Interactive Torture Machine
snippet.description: Interactive Torture Machine Rack up the highest pain score you can by leading the victim into variety of traps.

snippet.title: Impale 2
snippet.description: Impale 2 Physics puzzle. Shoot the zombies right at the machines that destroy them and get the light active.

snippet.title: Reel Gold
snippet.description: Reel Gold Make your fortune in the Hills, clear your pitch before the time runs out and the Gold Rush begins!

snippet.title: Rudolfs Revenge
snippet.description: Rudolfs Revenge It's time for revenge. Hit Santa to make him fly as high as possible. Left click to activate the elfs.

snippet.title: Elite Forces: Mission Afghanistan
snippet.description: Elite Forces: Mission Afghanistan You are stationed in Afghanistan, clear the area and wipe out all enemy forces.

snippet.title: William and Sly
snippet.description: William and Sly Platform adventure game. You are Sly the fox. Collect the fairyflies and activate the runestones.

snippet.title: Red Code 2
snippet.description: Red Code 2 Action shooter. Power on the beacons, clear the landing zone of the insects and kill the insect queen.

snippet.title: My Big Friend
snippet.description: My Big Friend Platform game. Find the crystals and you can travel through time opening portals to escape.

snippet.title: Temple Glider
snippet.description: Temple Glider Arcade game. Guide the bird through the egyptian temples and active the sarcophags to complete levels.
